{"lastModified":1761137345594,"uri":"c::7819256863::vessel::d5c9adde-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nVirtuoso is a stunning 34.6m luxury gulet yacht available for charter in Turkey and Greece. This exquisite motor sailor epitomizes the essence of luxury and elegance on the open seas, blending classic sailing aesthetics with modern motor-powered convenience.\n\nVirtuoso can accommodate up to 12 passengers in 6 beautifully designed cabins, ensuring comfort and elegance for all guests. The cabin configuration includes 1 master suite, 1 VIP cabin, and 4 double cabins, each featuring luxurious furnishings and modern amenities for a relaxing stay.\n\nHer timeless elegance is highlighted by sleek lines and a sophisticated silhouette, making her a true masterpiece on the water. The best of Bodrum-style woodworking is combined with state-of-the-art technology, offering an unparalleled yachting experience.\n\nTo ensure privacy and personalized service, Virtuoso has a dedicated crew area separate from the guest accommodations. The professional crew members are committed to providing five-star service, attending to every detail to make your trip unforgettable.\n\nVirtuoso offers ample space for leisure and recreation, with outstanding facilities that make her the perfect choice for entertaining family and friends. Guests can partake in a variety of water activities facilitated by the yacht’s extensive array of water toys and equipment, adding an extra layer of fun and adventure to your voyage.\n\nEmbark on a journey of luxury and comfort aboard Virtuoso, where exceptional craftsmanship meets modern innovation, delivering an exquisite charter experience.","blueprint":{"name":"VIRTUOSO","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5c9adde-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::cb28f400-be4e-11ef-976c-1b41e0fdb635/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5c9adde-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::881ccc9